---
title: Sơ đồ tuần tự — Khách hàng claim voucher (chống TOCTOU)
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor KH as Khách hàng
    participant FE as Frontend<br/>(Next.js /member)
    participant API as FastAPI<br/>router claim
    participant SVC as VoucherService
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    KH->>FE: bấm "Nhận ngay"
    FE->>+API: POST /campaigns/{id}/claim<br/>JWT + X-Tenant-Id
    API->>+SVC: claim(user_id, campaign_id)
    SVC->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION
    SVC->>DB: pg_advisory_xact_lock(hash(campaign_id))
    SVC->>DB: UPDATE campaign SET issued_count=issued_count+1<br/>WHERE id=? AND issued_count<max_issuances
    DB-->>SVC: rows_affected

    alt rows_affected = 1
        SVC->>DB: INSERT INTO voucher (code, member_id, ...)
        DB-->>SVC: voucher_id
        SVC->>DB: COMMIT
        SVC-->>API: Voucher DTO
        API-->>FE: 201 Created + voucher JSON
        FE-->>KH: hiển thị voucher mới
    else rows_affected = 0
        SVC->>DB: ROLLBACK
        SVC-->>API: CampaignQuotaExceededError
        API-->>FE: 409 Conflict
    end
    deactivate SVC
    deactivate API

    Note over SVC,DB: Advisory lock + atomic UPDATE guard<br/>đảm bảo không vượt max_issuances<br/>kể cả khi N request đồng thời.
